abstract: Intel benefited from a reorganization and various new products after several quarters of a bruising price war with Advanced Micro Devices.
snippet: Intel benefited from a reorganization and various new products after several quarters of a bruising price war with Advanced Micro Devices.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, Oct. 16 — Intel cheered investors on Tuesday when it reported better-than-expected quarterly sales and a 43 percent increase in profit on strong worldwide demand for personal computers.

headline.main: Intel, Buoyed by Quarter, Offers an Upbeat Outlook
headline.print_headline: Intel, Buoyed by Quarter, Offers an Upbeat Outlook
